data.description: Clifton plan on the cul de sac at lot 17 is a must see! Entering this immaculate home, you encounter a spacious formal dining. A wide foyer leads to huge family room with rod iron staircase. Featuring gleaming stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and tile backsplash. The kitchen has a spacious island overlooking a cozy breakfast area and family room into the fireplace. Upstairs, you will find 3 secondary bedrooms with vaulted ceilings and walk in closets! The oversized owner's retreat has a spa-like bathroom and cavernous closet! 2021-05-24
